{
  "id": "6a0af4b223bf49789d4844b9",
  "title": "昭和 (侮蔑語)",
  "created": 1779102978,
  "updated": 1779105366,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a0af4b223bf49789d4844b9",
      "text": "昭和 (侮蔑語)",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779102978,
      "updated": 1779102978
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af502000000000015726f",
      "text": "[時代区分]としての[元号]を侮蔑語・批判の表現として用いるのは不味いと思う[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779102978,
      "updated": 1779103399
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af63d0000000000157286",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103294,
      "updated": 1779103299
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0afe27000000000015728e",
      "text": "特に[女性蔑視]を批判する意図が強いことがわからない",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779105320,
      "updated": 1779105336
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0afe390000000000157290",
      "text": "\t[hoagecko.icon]としては「昭和」の語にはそれよりも戦時の無駄死にの印象が強い",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779105337,
      "updated": 1779105366
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0afe28000000000015728f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779105320,
      "updated": 1779105320
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af6430000000000157288",
      "text": "明治の[一世一元制]以降、天皇の一代と元号がリンクしているため、帝国の統治者としての昭和天皇の功績・問題に関連付けて用いるならアリ[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103299,
      "updated": 1779105299
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af63d0000000000157287",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103294,
      "updated": 1779103294
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af5410000000000157275",
      "text": "問題点",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103042,
      "updated": 1779103051
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af54b0000000000157276",
      "text": " 1. そもそも「昭和」が広すぎ問題",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103051,
      "updated": 1779103062
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af5550000000000157277",
      "text": " \t戦前の都市モダニズム文化",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103062,
      "updated": 1779103081
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af5f00000000000157280",
      "text": " \t[満州事変]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103217,
      "updated": 1779103238
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af5f60000000000157281",
      "text": " \t[二・二六事件]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103223,
      "updated": 1779103226
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af595000000000015727a",
      "text": " \t[日中戦争]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103126,
      "updated": 1779103230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af56b0000000000157278",
      "text": " \t[第二次世界大戦]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103083,
      "updated": 1779103236
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af599000000000015727b",
      "text": " \t[敗戦]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103130,
      "updated": 1779103234
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af59c000000000015727c",
      "text": " \t[GHQ]による占領",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103132,
      "updated": 1779103144
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af5ae000000000015727e",
      "text": " \t「[もはや戦後ではない]」",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103150,
      "updated": 1779103160
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af62d0000000000157284",
      "text": " \t[上を向いて歩こう]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103278,
      "updated": 1779103284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af5a8000000000015727d",
      "text": " \t[沖縄本土復帰]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103144,
      "updated": 1779103242
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af61a0000000000157283",
      "text": " \t[インベーダーブーム]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103258,
      "updated": 1779103270
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af6110000000000157282",
      "text": " \t[バブル景気]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103249,
      "updated": 1779103257
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af5c0000000000015727f",
      "text": " \t以上全てが「昭和」",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103169,
      "updated": 1779103248
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af6b60000000000157289",
      "text": " 2. 問題としている「昭和」がどこにあるのかわからない",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103414,
      "updated": 1779105235
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af63a0000000000157285",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103290,
      "updated": 1779103291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af6e4000000000015728c",
      "text": "[平成]もそのうち平成以後生まれに侮蔑語として使われるのだろうか…",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103461,
      "updated": 1779105229
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af6e4000000000015728d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103461,
      "updated": 1779103461
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af5350000000000157271",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103029,
      "updated": 1779103029
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af5380000000000157272",
      "text": "[昭和]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103032,
      "updated": 1779103034
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af6480000000000ba4447",
      "text": "[昭和的価値観]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1779103305,
      "updated": 1779103319
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af5380000000000157273",
      "text": "[侮蔑語]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103032,
      "updated": 1779103036
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0af53a0000000000157274",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1779103034,
      "updated": 1779103034
    }
  ]
}